    "description": "<strong>《星舰迷航》是一款尊重物理法则的宇宙飞船模拟游戏，你将在各个星球间穿梭、制作各式各样的物品、探索这片太空。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/8df187043f59b90c21a2e75f51497d54.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/8df187043f59b90c21a2e75f51497d54.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/8df187043f59b90c21a2e75f51497d54.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>对接臂与起重绳</strong><br>宇宙飞船安装有一副对接臂，可以精确地固定和移动物体；飞船底部有一根起重机绳，可以从星球表面将物品吊起。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/97c00ef6110a36ed11779f93033d9054.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/97c00ef6110a36ed11779f93033d9054.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/97c00ef6110a36ed11779f93033d9054.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/43a04783c64ddfc5123107f040ef9fcd.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/43a04783c64ddfc5123107f040ef9fcd.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/43a04783c64ddfc5123107f040ef9fcd.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>水晶与升级</strong><br>你可以收集水晶能量来为你的宇宙飞船加油、修理或升级。 涡轮推进、装甲、额外油箱、加固底盘等等……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/0d1039a38700ff344af38ee75ea71230.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/0d1039a38700ff344af38ee75ea71230.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/0d1039a38700ff344af38ee75ea71230.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/f0bf90112cd133be0a73bd4c43fd6520.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/f0bf90112cd133be0a73bd4c43fd6520.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/f0bf90112cd133be0a73bd4c43fd6520.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>启动发电机</strong><br>此外，水晶还可用于为发电机提供电能，启动各种机器或站点，这将帮助你传送到另一个星球或发送紧急信号寻求援助！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/f90450c3e8a497e7dce3e733d15b5b23.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/f90450c3e8a497e7dce3e733d15b5b23.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/f90450c3e8a497e7dce3e733d15b5b23.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/e266b94b6756a3050681eaa43aed29bb.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/e266b94b6756a3050681eaa43aed29bb.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/e266b94b6756a3050681eaa43aed29bb.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>广袤宇宙</strong><br>当你探索新的行星时，你可以发现更多的可采集资源。 制作更多物品来修复星球上的设施。每颗星球都有自己的特点！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/7961c0db0b26fd90342ef748abec89b8.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/7961c0db0b26fd90342ef748abec89b8.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/7961c0db0b26fd90342ef748abec89b8.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/0ea99c3ded29febc24cc0f033dfa8a62.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/0ea99c3ded29febc24cc0f033dfa8a62.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/0ea99c3ded29febc24cc0f033dfa8a62.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>主线故事</strong><br>我们的英雄汤姆发现自己被绑架到了一个未知的宙域，他必须在这个陌生的新世界中不断航行，揭开他被绑架的秘密，并最终找到返回地球的方法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/5131e87687d26a9a40822b35aaa24df2.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/5131e87687d26a9a40822b35aaa24df2.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/5131e87687d26a9a40822b35aaa24df2.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
